## Summary
This documentation explains how Amplitude defines and tracks user sessions across mobile and web applications, including session ID generation, timeout behaviors, and custom session definition options. It details how to implement session tracking through SDKs or HTTP API, handle out-of-session events, and configure custom session properties for analysis.

